originalText: You wouldn't survive for a second in the Arena with skills like that.
A rookie could do more than that!
It's gonna take more than that...
Did you think that would blow me up, hah!
This pain... It won't break me down!
The pain! It drives me forward!
You... you're bringing forth the Revelation without your own consent!
Argh! I'll carry this scar forever... Small price to pay.
Argh... this pain... it drives me forward.
Blood... a small price to pay.
::Covers the wound.:: That won't... stop me.
I'll reduce you to ashes for this!
We have seen the truth! Argh!
You cannot hide... from what is to come!
My brain is being crushed! Ugggh!
I took a hundred of those back in there.
The pain... Argh! I'll never bow down.
Umpf! I... I'll break away from this prison!
My legs... I must... keep going... forward...
Foul things, argh! Where is... you courage, coward!
The pain won't... cloud my mind...
We made it this far... W-we... ::Coughs.::
Dare put me on fire! This will be your fate soon! Argh!
This was not... meant to happen!
Put it out! Put it out!
::Frantically tries to pat the fire out.::
Our goal... brrr... is so close...
::Struggles to move.:: I'll break free from... this, argh!
I wanna see you all DIE!
My mind is pure... but my body...
This will not... poison my mind!
Their filthy money, their crooked offerings! Ahhhhh!
Not another... match in there... Stop this!
The carnage... of DomiNation... The Revelation... Save us!
Broken rib? Not the first one!
::Grabs chest.:: I... I can still do this...
No! Get out... GET OUT OF MY... HEEEEEAAAAD!
Oh, you won't have me. You! Won't! Have! Meeeee-heheh!
Brrrr! Grrrr! There is an intruder in my... my... mind! Aaargh!
Blood? It... argh! It wont stop me!
The bleeding... I... can take it!
The trash below is a suitable grave for the likes of you!
Your corpse will decorate the sewers below!
I'll place the final charge in your smashed skull!
Time has come to Dominate the Dominated!
The trash below... calls to you.
The Revelation was true, we have won!
The filth above will soon join you... in death.
You cannot save the ignorant above.
One final wrong to undo it all...
Open your eyes... for the last time.
The Master has taught us well. His explosions will make short work of you.
Stay awake... to see it all go down.
The lack of focus and vision... It shows.
There's nothing wrong with having a little poison in your blood.
Don't stop the bleeding, it's good for ya!
Stop trying... there is no saving them now.
If only you knew what happened in there...
A missed opportunity. We all were.
One of many I had to take to overcome challenges!
All patched up and ready for the final challenge!
Yeees! Soon it will all be undone!
Food and games... To end all food and games!
I fall... in the ring of... battle...
Food and games... will go... on...
We failed to stop... the food and games...
Time to end food and games!
Time to bring the entire ring down!
We'll bring down all the decadent.
Depraved of mind do not deserve to live!
Dissoluted mindless beasts! We'll put them down!
I'll beat you to a bloody pulp!
My hammer will put an end to all of the corrupt!
Many challengers have felt the weight of this bad boy. ::Raises hammer.::
I'll slam you all the way down to the sewers!
I'll swipe away all the filth!
I'll carve you up like a mushroom cake!
Let's put a bloody smile on that face!
Say hello to my little friend!
This bullet's got your name on it!
Your pile of ash will descent on the trash below. ::Laughs.::
Welcome to the green side of life...
I'll turn you into red swill!
See if you can catch this!
I'll pin you to a wall!
I've got the bolt just for you!
A battle of the minds incoming!
I'll crush your puny little mind!
I'll turn your brain to mush!
The cheering for bloodbath... will be over soon.
Now you see me, now you don't.
I don't know why, but the word "hypothermia" just springs to my mind...
Do you like your bones chilled?
I hope you're wearing something warm.
You are gonna be so cool. ::Laughs.::
How about I burn that smile off your face!?
Let's heat things up a bit...
I hope you'll enjoy this warm reception...
I need cover! We cannot fail!
Aid me! We must finish this!
These are the final moments of your life.
This is going right through you!
I'm gonna chop you into pieces!
I'll blow your head to bits!
